&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;公式&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
v_0=\begin{cases}+V_{CC} &amp;amp; A(v_p-v_n)\gt V_{CC} \\
A(v_p-v_n) &amp;amp; -V_{CC}\le A(v_p-v_n) \le +V_{CC} \\ -V_{CC} &amp;amp; A(v_p-v_n) \lt -V_{CC}\end{cases}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;反相放大器电路&#34;&gt;反相放大器电路&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;图示&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;655&#34;
	height=&#34;458&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/1_hua0d969c29aa687c1dcb4a19c345540cd_66788_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/1_hua0d969c29aa687c1dcb4a19c345540cd_66788_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;143&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;343px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;推导&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
i_f+i_s=i_n = 0 \\\
\\ v_n=v_p=0 \\\
\\ \frac{v_0}{R_f}+\frac{v_s}{R_s} = 0\\\
\\ \therefore v_0=-\frac{R_f}{R_s}v_s \\\
\\ |v_0|\le V_{CC}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;求和放大器电路&#34;&gt;求和放大器电路&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;图示-1&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;764&#34;
	height=&#34;393&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/2_hud0394457d426dffc405dcc13d9ef0ada_68531_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/2_hud0394457d426dffc405dcc13d9ef0ada_68531_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;194&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;466px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;推导-1&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
通过节点电压法可以得到 \\\
\\ v_0=-(\frac{R_f}{R_a}v_a+\frac{R_f}{R_b}v_b+\frac{R_f}{R_c}v_c) \\\
\\ 若R_a=R_b=R_c=R_s \\\
\\ v_0=-\frac{R_f}{R_s}(v_a+v_b+v_c) \\\
\\ 若R_f=R_S \\\
\\ v_0=v_a+v_b+v_c，输入与输出电压正好反相
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;同相放大器电路&#34;&gt;同相放大器电路&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;图示-2&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;711&#34;
	height=&#34;453&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/3_hu6c551b2854c55a1a8657a7cade023d21_62468_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/3_hu6c551b2854c55a1a8657a7cade023d21_62468_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;156&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;376px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;推导-2&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\frac{v_0-v_n}{R_f}+\frac{v_n}{R_s}=0\\\
\\ v_0=\frac{R_f+R_S}{R_s}v_n
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;差分放大器&#34;&gt;差分放大器&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;图示-3&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;752&#34;
	height=&#34;446&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/4_hu15c65a03ecc90accab71351ee7bb5d0d_78692_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://example.com/p/%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/4_hu15c65a03ecc90accab71351ee7bb5d0d_78692_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;168&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;404px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;推导-3&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
对于反相节点\\\
\\ \frac{v_n-v_a}{R_A}+\frac{v_0-v_n}{R_b}= 0 \\\
\\ 对于同相节点 \\\
\\ v_p=\frac{R_d}{R_c+R_d}v_b = v_n \\\
\\ \Rightarrow v_0=\frac{R_d(R_a+R_b)}{R_a(R_c+R_d)}v_b-\frac{R_b}{R_a}v_a\\\
\\ 当\frac{R_a}{R_b}=\frac{R_c}{R_d} \\\
\\ v_0=\frac{R_b}{R_a}(v_b-v_a)
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;关于差分放大器的其他问题&#34;&gt;关于差分放大器的其他问题&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;共模输入与差模输入&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
v_{dm} = v_b-v_a \\\
\\ v_{cm} = \frac{v_a+v_b}{2} \\\
\\ \therefore v_0=A_{cm}v_{cm}+A_{dm}v_{dm} \\\
\\ 当R_a=R_c，R_b=R_d \\\
\\ v_0 = (o)v_{cm}+\frac{R_b}{R_a}v_{dm}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
